(8, 0, 0, 'lgnForgotPassTpl', '', 0, 3, 0, '<div class="loginFPErrors">[[+loginfp.errors]]</div>\n<div class="loginFP">\n    <form class="loginFPForm" action="/[[~[[*id]]]]" method="post">\n        <fieldset class="loginFPFieldset">\n        	<input class="returnUrl" type="hidden" name="returnUrl" value="[[+loginfp.request_uri]]" />\n          <input class="loginFPService" type="hidden" name="login_fp_service" value="forgotpassword" />\n          <ul>\n          	<li>\n              <label class="loginFPUsernameLabel">[[%register.email]]</label>\n              <input class="loginFPUsername" type="text" name="username" value="[[+loginfp.post.username]]" />\n            </li>\n            <li class="button">\n            	<span class="loginFPButton"><input type="submit" name="login_fp" value="[[%login.reset_password]]" /></span>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </fieldset>\n    </form>\n</div>', 0, 'a:0:{}', 0, ''),
(9, 0, 0, 'lgnResetPassTpl', '', 0, 3, 0, '<div class="loginResetPass">\n<p class="loginResetPassText">Пароль изменен. <a href="/[[+loginUrl]]">Войти</a>.</p>  \n</div>', 0, 'a:0:{}', 0, ''),
(10, 0, 0, 'lgnRegisterForm', '', 0, 3, 0, '<div class="register order-form">\n    <div class="registerMessage">[[+error.message]]</div>\n    \n    <form class="form" action="/[[~[[*id]]]]" method="post">\n        <input type="hidden" name="nospam:blank" value="" />\n        \n        <ul>\n        	<li>\n        		<label for="firstname">[[%register.firstname? &namespace=`login` &topic=`register`]]\n            <span class="error">[[+error.firstname]]</span>\n        		</label>\n        		<input type="text" name="firstname:required" id="firstname" value="[[+firstname]]" />\n        	</li>\n        	<li>\n        		<label for="lastname">[[%register.lastname? &namespace=`login` &topic=`register`]]\n            <span class="error">[[+error.lastname]]</span>\n        		</label>\n        		<input type="text" name="lastname" id="lastname" value="[[+lastname]]" />\n        	</li>\n        	<li>\n		        <label for="email">[[%register.email]]\n		            <span class="error">[[+error.email]]</span>\n		        </label>\n		        <input type="email" name="email" id="email" value="[[+email]]" />\n        	</li>\n        	<li>\n		        <label for="phone">[[%register.phone]]\n		            <span class="error">[[+error.phone]]</span>\n		        </label>\n		        <input type="phone" name="phone" id="phone" value="[[+phone]]" placeholder="[[%register.phone_format]]"/>\n        	</li>\n        	<li>\n		        <label for="password">[[%register.password]]\n		            <span class="error">[[+error.password]]</span>\n		        </label>\n		        <input type="password" name="password:required" id="password" value="[[+password]]" />\n		      </li>\n        	<li>\n		        <label for="password_confirm">[[%register.password_confirm]]\n		            <span class="error">[[+error.password_confirm]]</span>\n		        </label>\n		        <input type="password" name="password_confirm" id="password_confirm" value="[[+password_confirm]]" />\n		        <br class="clear" />\n		        [[+register.recaptcha_html]]\n        		[[+error.recaptcha]]\n		      </li>\n        	<li class="button">\n            <input type="submit" name="login-register-btn" value="[[%register.register]]" />\n          </li>\n				</ul>\n    </form>\n</div>', 0, 'a:0:{}', 0, ''),
(11, 0, 0, 'lgnActivateEmailTpl', '', 0, 3, 0, '\n\n<p>Вы были зарегистрированы на сайте Студии дизайна TesoriCasa.</p>\n\n<p>Для подтверждения регистрации пройдите по ссылке:</p>\n\n<p><a href="[[+confirmUrl]]">[[+confirmUrl]]</a></p>\n\n<p>После подтверждения вы сможете войти на сайт:</p>\n\n<p>\nЛогин: <strong>[[+email]]</strong><br />\nПароль: <strong>[[+password]]</strong></p>\n\n<br />\n\n<p><em>С уважением, администрация сайта TesoriCasa.ru</em></p>', 0, 'a:0:{}', 0, ''),
